Hey there Alex. My nick is Yutaka in Innoruuk. I'm a level 8 monk. I play on Friday and Saturday. Based in Qeynos ;-)

I am looking for netted gloves because Mr Muron loves to lure scarecrows to me <Scarecrows are magic only creatures>.

I am more of a solo-ist unless I find the right patient partner. Also, I talk too much.

<grins>

Wilson
